    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a high heat and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, give it a good mix up</p><p>Reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 13-16 min or until the rice is cooked</p><p>Tip: Stir halfway through, to stop it sticking!</p>",
