    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> with a small knob of <strong>butter </strong>(don't stir!), then put the lid back on</p><p>Set aside, for 4-6 min or until the peas are warmed through</p><p>Once the peas are warmed through, give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>halloumi jambalaya with pepper & peas</strong></p>",
